These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite, water
House: craftsman, art-deco, wooden, tower
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the tower house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
3. the craftsman house is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
5. the craftsman house is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | sprite |
| House   | wooden | tower      | craftsman | art-deco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, mirinda, 7up
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goat, horse
1. the person drinking soy-milk is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the horse##2
2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | 7up | mirinda | soy-milk   | hot-chocolate |
| Pet           | goat      | bird    | chinchilla | horse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, peach, potato
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, collecting, card-games, cooking
1. the person eating corn is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##5
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | corn | cabbage | peach     | potato |
| Hobby   | collecting  | cooking   | card-games | chess    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
4 different games are played: backgammon, domino, bridge, go
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person playing go and the person playing domino##2
4. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
5. the person playing go is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | card-games | singing | woodworking |
| Game   | go   | bridge     | domino    | backgammon       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, car, bike, scooter
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, western, zombie
1. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
3. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
6. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Transport          | bike | scooter   | quad-bike   | car    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | zombie | disaster | western |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, firefighter, paramedic, police-officer
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, white, ebony, grey
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the person who likes grey##5
3. the person who likes grey is between the police-officer and the person who likes ebony##2
4. the paramedic is on the right of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Job           | electrician | firefighter | police-officer | paramedic |
| Color   | ebony        | grey     | brown       | white   |

