.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, mango, pear, strawberry
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bluemaster, swisher, tiparillo
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the swisher-smoker##5
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food   | mango     | strawberry | pear     | carrot   |
| Cigar    | tiparillo | bluemaster  | swisher | pall-mall |

