.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, parkour, water-polo, baseball
There 4 different types of food: lemon, pear, potato, tomato
1. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
5. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
6. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Sport   | badminton | water-polo | baseball   | parkour |
| Food       | lemon       | potato   | tomato | pear |

