.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, polish, colombian, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, surfing, water-polo, weightlifting
1. the colombian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
4. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
5. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian       | dutch   | malaysian        |
| Sport      | surfing  | weightlifting | soccer | water-polo |

