.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, epic, crime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, soul, trance
1. the fan of gospel is the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the right of the fan of ambient##5
3. the fan of gospel is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the left of the fan of trance##5
5. the fan of trance is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
6. the person watching crime movies is the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | epic | crime | comedy | animation |
| Music-Genre   | ambient     | trance  | gospel  | soul    |

