.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, milk, 7up
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, canadian, mexican
1. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the american##5
3. the brazilian is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the mexican is the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
6. the brazilian is on the left or right of the american##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up  | almond-milk | water | milk |
| Nationality   | canadian | american | brazilian   | mexican  |

