.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
City: rome, venice, prague, marseilles
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, entrepreneur, manager, mechanic
1. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to venice##2
2. the analyst is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
3. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
5. the manager is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
6. the manager is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| City   | rome | prague  | marseilles      | venice |
| Job     | manager    | mechanic | entrepreneur | analyst   |

