.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, emerald, green, yellow
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, taxi, tram
1. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
2. the person who likes green is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Color   | red     | emerald | yellow | green |
| Transport     | helicopter | bike    | taxi    | tram |

