.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, rock-climbing, chess, reading
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
3. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | milk     | soy-milk | cola     | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby   | chess | reading  | dancing | rock-climbing        |

