.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, martial-arts, superhero
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person watching animation movies is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person watching fantasy movies##2
2. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
5. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre         | martial-arts   | superhero   | animation       | fantasy   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | jet-ski | helicopter | snowmobile |

