.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, grapes, strawberry, watermelon
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, ranch-style, victorian
1. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the victorian house##1
3. the ranch-style house is in an odd position##4
4. the craftsman house is somewhere to the right of the gothic-revival house##5
5. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
6. the person eating asparagus is between the person eating watermelon and the craftsman house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | grapes     | watermelon | asparagus | strawberry |
| House   | ranch-style | victorian | gothic-revival      | craftsman        |

 